MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

92-1401. State ex rel. Brofford v. Fourth Dist. Court of Appeals.

In Procedendo. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of procedendo. Upon consideration of relator’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective August 19, 1992.
